# kaiiak — Project Context

Multi-sport social app for all active people in Quebec. Domain: kaiiak.com

- **Scope**: not running-only — all outdoor sports (running, road cycling, mountain biking, kayak, yoga, hiking, swimming, cross-country skiing, snowshoeing, skating). Not a dating app — for everyone who wants to move outside together.
- **Concept**: people sign up for outdoor activities together. They meet at a "point de chute" (park, café, landmark), the group does the activity together. Afterward, "Apéro Smoothie" at a nearby café.
- **Features**: buddy codes (ANIMAL-MOT format) for pairing with friends; sub-groups for large events; threshold system (min 6 to confirm); multiple Organisateurs per event; paid activities (on-site payment); recurring events (weekly, biweekly, monthly, custom days).
- **Models (domain)**: `KaiEvent` (not RunDateEvent), `IntensityLevel` (not PaceLabel), `UserActivity` (sport + level per user), `ActivityMatch`.
- **Tone**: casual "tu" (tutoiement), natural Québécois French, encouraging, light and fun
- **Stack**: Monorepo — Flutter mobile app (`apps/mobile/`), Next.js web app (`apps/web/`, planned), Django backend (`backend/`, planned)
- **Data**: all data is currently mocked (no backend connected)
- **Matching**: described as AI-powered — no actual algorithm yet
- **Theme**: teal-to-navy gradient (logo colors: #00D4AA → #00BCD4 → #0097A7 → #1B2A4A) on cream background (#FBF7F2 light, #1A1A2E dark). Nunito titles, DM Sans body.
- **UX rule**: one question per screen in wizards, never overload the user
- **Labels**: `IntensityLevel` — Chill, Relax, Modéré, Intense, Extrême. `DistanceLabel` — Courte, Moyenne, Longue, Très longue, Ultra.
